’Щ@91462044bad824e86eae12aeb9d72e11b75d0b47d2fba535326f8f3f74eb05d6ЪTitle: title: polars explode
Path: Examples
Content:
Explode the specified dataframe
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[id name hobbies]; [1 Mercy [Cycling Knitting]] [2 Bob [Skiing Football]]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars explode hobbies
                    | polars collect
                    | polars sort-by [id, name]
